        &lt;/p&gt;
       &lt;/li&gt;
       &lt;li&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;
         &lt;input type="checkbox"/&gt;
         Gain familiarity with machine learning algorithms and their practical applications.
        &lt;/p&gt;
       &lt;/li&gt;
       &lt;li&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;
         &lt;input type="checkbox"/&gt;
